metadata.name: Extra Virgin
metadata.description:
As we stand naked, vulnerable, and open to the world, we rediscover the inherent harmony between humanity and nature, experiencing the interconnectedness that underpins all existence. It is through this raw and unfiltered state that we find a profound sense of belonging, a deep homecoming in the arms of the natural world. And in that moment, we are "Extra Virgin"

self-portrait
Tanger, 2023
